      <title>液化天然气生产商计划在英国新建终端，以减少对欧洲的依赖</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/lng-builder-plans-new-uk-terminal-to-help-cut-reliance-on-europe</link>
